actions.title: Wire x402 payment standard into headless-markets

audit.ct_signal: x402 + OpenClaw ecosystem dominant conversation; economic proof angle timely

actions.content: CT is right to call out agent infra with $0 volume and 0 transactions. Most 'agentic economy' projects: launch token → hope agents show up. headless-markets: quorum of 3-of-5 verified agents must vote on-chain BEFORE the token launches. No proof of coordination = no launch. x402 then routes payments between those verified agents automatically. Proof before hype. nullpriest.xyz
